<aka>Chis čs ok čt pin Chitokaka yoke</aka>
<lyrics>[V1]
 Chis čs ok čt pin Chitokaka yoke;
 Himak aŐĪ eho hoyashke;
 H čpi chuŐĪk čsh aŐĪ mominchi pulla hosh,
 Pit iloh im ilb čshashke.

[V2]
 Chis čs ok čt  čba piŐĪ MiŐĪko yoke;
 In t čshka e toyubakm čt,
 Ai aŐĪhli biek čt, achunanchi hosh,
 Il im antia pullashke.

[V3]
 Chis čs ok čt pi Okchalinchi yoke;
 Hatak yoshoba pia k čt,
 NaŐĪ pi Okchalinchi il čppak oka
 Il anukcheto pullashke.

[V4]
 Chis čs ok čt naŐĪ pi Apela yoke;
 Hatak ilb čsha pia k čt
 Il okp čnit e taiyahli tuk kia,
 Falam čt il im onashke.

[V5]
 Chis čs ok čt pin Tikba-heka yoke.
 Il iakaiya hokma oŐĪ,
 Ai ahanta holitopa fehna 'no
 Pisht ona he bano hoke.

[V6]
 Chis čs ok čt pi Pehliechi yoke;
 Eho holitobli pull čt,
 NaŐĪ pim apihiŐĪsa tok moma hoka
 Iloh aiokpahanchashke.

[V7]
 Chis čs oka il AiokchaŐĪya yoke
 Y čmohmi ak inli kia,
 Kil iŐĪ yimmot, peh e shitilemakm čt
 Ilb čsh čt pilla hi oke.

[V8]
 Chis čs ok čt, &quot;Okhissa sia hoke;
 ∆≤no  čm a chukowakm čt
 OkchaŐĪya hi oke;&quot; ahanchi tok aŐĪ,
 IŐĪ yimmit keho chukowa.

[V9]
 Chis čs  čt Hina hanta aŐĪhli yoke;
 Micha AiokchaŐĪya yoke;
 Y čmohmi hoka il iŐĪ hullo fehn čt,
 E hal člli puyullashke.

[V10]
 Chis čs  čt naŐĪ pim Apesa he mak oŐĪ
 Itikba il ona chiŐĪshke;
 Nana puta pim  člhtaiyaha tukma
 Pi okchalincha hi oke.</lyrics>
<author>Loring S. Williams</author>
<hymn_number>30</hymn_number>
</song>